Project Title 

Digital Detective: Mystery Investigation Adventure Game 

Description 
Digital Detective is a mystery investigation game where the player acts as a detective and 
solves different criminal cases by collecting clues, analyzing evidence, and solving puzzles. 
Each level introduces a new case with increasing difficulty. The goal is to improve logical 
thinking and problem-solving skills through interactive gameplay. 

Resources 
□ Java Programming Language 
□ Java Swing (GUI Development) 
□ NetBeans IDE 
□ File Handling (No Database) 
□ Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) 
□ Images & Sound Assets 

Steps 
[1] Create game window and main menu. 
[2] Design detective character and interface. 
[3] Add movement system for player. 
[4] Create investigation maps/rooms. 
[5] Add clue collection system. 
[6] Implement puzzle-solving mechanics. 
[7] Add score system. 
[8] Save progress using files. 
[9] Test and debug game. 

